Text: Board MeetingHello Everyone Just a friendly reminder that our next Board Meeting is scheduled for next Tuesday October th at am in the Glass Room Please let me know if you will be attending You may call me at or email me at You should be receiving your Board Meeting packet in the mail Please remember to bring your packet with you on Tuesday I will have a few extra packets made up in case someone should forget theirs I look forward to meeting everyone on Tuesday Lori Bennett
